title: SCTV reunion at Museum of Television and Radio
description:
This is the most amusing of the SCTV reunion shows that I&#039;ve seen, although I don&#039;t believe it ever aired on TV.

In addition to several other cast and crew members who frequently got together again over the years, Rick Moranis, Dave Thomas, and the one person on the panel who doesn&#039;t even get to talk -- Robin Duke also appeared in this one, but they weren&#039;t in the other reunions (at least not those featured on the DVDs).
